components.name: Load and Modify Data
components.description: Ingests stations.csv, parses installation_date, standardizes location names, and converts the data to JSON using the load-and-modify service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

connections.purpose: Shared data directory mounted into containers

components.name: Geocode Reconciliation
components.description: Geocodes station locations by adding latitude and longitude to the JSON data using the reconciliation service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: OpenMeteo Data Extension
components.description: Retrieves historical weather variables from OpenMeteo based on latitude, longitude, and installation date, appending them to the dataset. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Land Use Extension
components.description: Adds land use classification to each record using a GIS API based on latitude and longitude. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Population Density Extension
components.description: Appends population density information for the area surrounding each station location using a demographic data service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Environmental Risk Calculation
components.description: Computes a custom environmental risk score from precipitation, population density, and land use type, adding the result as a new column. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

connections.purpose: Docker network for internal service calls

components.name: Save Final Data
components.description: Exports the enriched environmental dataset to a CSV file using the save service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.
